title: [Ladies of the Night]
description: Large swaths of silk frame the interior of the circular tent in the mottled hues of the night.  From the high center, a chandelier of black sapphires glistens brightly.  In one corner, a raven-haired mannequin lounges casually against the wall.  Opposite the mannequin, a life-size silver wire figurine assumes a pose of feigned surprise.  In the center of the room, a slender doll woven from willow branches lies supine in a bed of colorful pillows.
